:PATH
Blix, Wash, and Stabilize
Pour out developer at exactly 3:15.
|
:INFO
Blix, Wash, and Stabilize
Pour out developer at exactly 3:15. Immediately pour in blix at 102 F. Agitate \
continuously for the first minute, then 4 inversions every 30 seconds. At 6:30, pour out \
blix. Wash with running water for 3 minutes (or three fill-and-dump cycles with 30

